{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_06_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 掴めない感覚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタイン前のある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――One day before Valentine's Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ここの振付は、当日のステージ規模を考えると……\nカメラワークも確認したいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The choreography here‚ considering the stage size on the day…\nI also want to check the camera work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依、お疲れ様",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui‚ good job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん。お疲れ様です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ Hello.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すみれはさっき駅まで見送りに行ったよ。優はもうすぐ\nソロの仕事が終わるから、この後迎えに行くつもりだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire just went to see off someone at the station earlier.\nI'm going to pick Yu up after her solo job is finished soon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "いつもありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you as always.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタイン当日のスペシャルライブの準備はどうだ？\n最近練習の様子を見れてなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are the preparations for the Valentine's Day special live going?\nI haven't been able to see the practice lately‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.2000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "順調ですよ。今はステージに合わせた細かい調整を\n考えていたところです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's going smoothly. Right now‚\nI'm thinking about fine-tuning to match the stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.4333341598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "なので、ステージングの方は大丈夫なんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the staging should be fine‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　他に悩みがあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Is there something else bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……その、バレンタインの新曲とCM撮影で\n行き詰まっていることがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I've been stuck with the new Valentine's Day song\nand the CM shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "撮影は、キスシーンのことで悩んでたよな\nでも、曲の方でも悩みがあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were worried about the kissing scene in the shoot‚ right?\nBut‚ do you also have concerns about the new song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.3666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "はい。どちらも気持ちが……\n自分の想いが乗り切らない感覚があるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I have mixed feelings about both…\nI have this feeling that my own emotions aren't coming through.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333341598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "CMの方向性も、新曲の方向性も\n男女のイベントのイメージが強いですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The direction of the CM and the new song both give off a strong image\nof a romantic event between a man and a woman.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.9666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、私はお付き合いしたり\n告白した経験もありません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ I've never dated anyone or\nconfessed my feelings before.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "恋愛小説などを読んで、演技や歌唱の表現を\n考えてきたんですが……うまくいかなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been reading romance novels and trying to think about\nhow to express acting and singing… but it's not going well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1333341598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "私、思ってみれば\nバレンタインって馴染みが薄いのかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've come to realize that Valentine's Day might not be\nsomething I'm familiar with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "母や優、すみれにチョコレートをあげたことは\nありましたけど、男性にあげたことはないので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My mother‚ Yu-chan‚ and Sumire-chan have received chocolates\nfrom me before‚ but I've never given any to a man.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（そうか、朝倉さんとは瑠依が小さい頃に……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see‚ Rui's childhood with Asakura-san…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "分かった、じゃあレッスンが終わり次第送るよ\n話の続きはそこでしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ once the lesson is over‚ I'll send you there.\nLet's continue our conversation then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "え……でも、優のお迎えはいいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… But‚ is it okay to pick up Yu-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "優の現場が終わるまで時間があるから大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay because there's time until Yu's job is finished.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.2666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.2666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.9666674931
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 117.9666674931
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、さっきの続きを聞かせてくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ can you continue from earlier?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.0333341598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタイン当日、学校のみんなが\nやけにそわそわしているのは分かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "On Valentine's Day‚ I noticed that everyone at school\nseemed unusually restless.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.1333341598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.9333341598
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "だけど、休み時間は次の授業の準備をしてますし\n放課後はすぐレッスンや仕事に向かっていたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ during breaks‚ I was busy preparing for the next class‚\nand after school‚ I headed straight to lessons and work…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2666674931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタイン自体が、どうも他人事に思えてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Valentine's Day itself somehow felt like something distant to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.1000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 141.9333341598
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "分かるよ。アイドルとして忙しくしてると\nどうしても周りと距離が出来るんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand.\nBeing busy as an idol can create distance from others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.3000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 148.3000008265
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_01-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "はい。それに経験で言えば、むしろ女子から\nもらうことの方が多かったくらいで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In my experience‚\nI've received chocolates from girls more often.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4000008265,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-night",
      "startTime": 155.1666674931
    },
